    • Class it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.Game

      class Game extends Object implements Serializable
      serialVersionUID:
      8587966332955395580L

      • Serialized Fields

        • characterCards
          Map<Character,Integer> characterCards
          Stores the 3 character cards selected for this game and the number of times they've been used
        • currentRound
          Round currentRound
          Stores the current round that is being played
        • defaultInfluenceCalculator
          InfluenceCalculator defaultInfluenceCalculator
          InfluenceCalculator used by default when calculating influence of a player on an island
        • expertMode
          boolean expertMode
          Whether the game is played with experto mode on
        • gameState
          Game.State gameState
          Stores the current game state (@see Game.State)
        • islands
          List<Island> islands
          Stores all the islands of this game. The last one is "connected" with the first one in a circular path.
        • motherNaturePosition
          int motherNaturePosition
          Stores the current mother nature position (index relative to the islands list)
        • numberOfPlayers
          int numberOfPlayers
          Desired number of players of this game, decided when game is created
        • players
          ArrayList<Player> players
          Stores the players of this game
        • professors
          Map<Student,Player> professors
          Stores for each student color which player has the professor, it is empty when the game is started
        • studentsBag
          RandomizedStudentsContainer studentsBag
          The students bag used to pick random students throughout the game
        • temporaryInfluenceCalculator
          InfluenceCalculator temporaryInfluenceCalculator
          One-shot InfluenceCalculator used when calculating influence of a player on an island under a character card effect. It has higher priority than defaultInfluenceCalculator
        • uuid
          UUID uuid
          Stores the unique id of this game
        • winner
          Player winner
          Used to retrieve the winner of this game, it is null until the game comes in the FINISHED state
